Easy to Install
===============
In your HTML, create an empty div like this:
<div id="feed1"></div>

And in you javascript, add this code:
$(document).ready(function(){
	$('#feed1').rssWidget({
		feedURL: 'http://feeds.feedburner.com/readwriteweb'
	});
});

Highly Configurable
===================
You can modify: 
-the format of the dates (including the name of the months)
-the HTML structure of the feed items that are shown, via the feedItemMarkup option
-the styles, via the (highly commented) CSS file
-You can install as many RSSWidgets as You want into the same site, at least have a different feedURL option for each one of them
-the maximum number of news items to show on each feed, via the maxItems option

Compatible
==========
Tested in Internet Explorer 6,7,8, Firefox 2,3 (Mac & PC), Safari, Chrome and Opera.

